            <li>Jump from plugin.xml action/extension ref to plugin class(supports Java, Kotlin) and vise versa.</li>
        </ul>
        <h2>1.0</h2>
        <ul>
            <li>initial release, add description and change-notes HTML editing support.</li>
        </ul>
